1. 把下载的Flatabulous-master.zip文件解压到"/usr/share/themes/"目录. 
		(https://github.com/anmoljagetia/Flatabulous/archive/master.zip)
2. 安装Icon主题(ultra-flat-icons):
		sudo add-apt-repository ppa:noobslab/icons
		sudo apt-get update
		sudo apt-get install ultra-flat-icons
3. 通过Ubuntu tweak tool将主题设定为Flatabulous, icons设定为ultra-flat.
